    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179170/extras/5972a089be7bdeec728ac9f5bc70174d.avif?t=1769025775\" width=800 height=226 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready for an exciting journey through with Mo and Fro? You’ll take on various levels all across a platitude of worlds. There's no task too dangerous or strange for this busy team of go-getters... unless you play with friends and families! Achieve record times! Solve challenging puzzles and have a blast with your partner in crime! We're stronger when connected. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master unique and connected character abilities at every new level. Help each other across an abundance of unexpected obstacles and laugh-out-loud moments.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Co-op!!</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invite a friend to join with Remote Play Together**, and experience a thrilling adventure built purely for two. Choose from couch or online co-op with shared-screen play, and face ever-changing challenges where working and being connected is the only way forward. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You need to be close and help each other clear a level.<br><br><strong>Character Abilities</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mo can Use Burrows.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179170/extras/fae41df15604e39541b0b07f0d2249ea.poster.avif?t=1769025775\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179170/extras/fae41df15604e39541b0b07f0d2249ea.webm?t=1769025775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179170/extras/fae41df15604e39541b0b07f0d2249ea.mp4?t=1769025775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mo can move blocks so that Fro can jump over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179170/extras/786dbf2340b896b0d5a097c4b887b85f.poster.avif?t=1769025775\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179170/extras/786dbf2340b896b0d5a097c4b887b85f.webm?t=1769025775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179170/extras/786dbf2340b896b0d5a097c4b887b85f.mp4?t=1769025775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fro can pick up objects to clear obstacles. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179170/extras/61185ad6f8cf9e367cecc2fa4f294ad2.poster.avif?t=1769025775\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179170/extras/61185ad6f8cf9e367cecc2fa4f294ad2.webm?t=1769025775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179170/extras/61185ad6f8cf9e367cecc2fa4f294ad2.mp4?t=1769025775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >World Mechanics <br> <br>Experience different worlds, each with its own set of mechanics you must navigate through with your partner, will you be able to clear them?  <br>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>New Game Plus</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After completing each world, you unlock an extra set of levels to play through with additional features included like a timer!</p>",
